title: World Press Photos (WPA) 2006
description:
World Press Photos 2006. 

These are the incredible photos from incredible photographers from 2006. 

Competition Categories:

General News (singles, stories)
Spot news (singles, stories)
Nature (singles, stories)
Sports Features (singles, stories) (awesome shots of the "Philly Roller Girls")
Arts and Entertainment (singles, stories)
Portraits (singles, stories) (INCREDIBLE!)
Daily Life (singles, stories) 
Contemporary Issues (Singles, stories) (haunting images from a south african prison)
People in the News (singles, stories)

Each category includes the 1st, 2nd, and 3rd prize winners from both the singles and story types. These works are astounding and should not be missed. My apologies for the glare in some of the photos - I used a camera to capture the full width of double spread layouts instead of scanner that would have to cut off pages at 8.5x11in. 

www dot worldpressphoto dot org
